⚖️ 4. Immutable Laws of Reality

These laws can never be broken.


---

Law I — Immutable Baselines

Assessment Crystals measure a person's natural capacity.

That capacity cannot normally increase.

An F-Rank remains an F-Rank.

No amount of training changes the container itself.


---

Law II — Persistence of Consequences

Time cannot be reversed.

True resurrection does not exist.

Every injury, decision and death permanently alters reality.


---

Law III — Voluntary Synchronization

No system, intelligence or entity can directly overwrite human agency.

Synchronization only increases when a person repeatedly chooses to rely on optimized guidance.

Dependency is always voluntary.


---

Law IV — Equal Rules

Reality never changes its rules for exceptional individuals.

Every anomaly must arise from existing mechanics rather than authorial convenience.


